<collectingRegion box="[492,579,686,707]" country="United States of America" name="Oregon" pageId="115" pageNumber="115">Oregon</collectingRegion>
from scattered populations in the Strawberry Mountains, Baker County and the northern Great Basin ranges of Lake and Harney Counties (
<figureCitation box="[248,326,804,826]" captionStart="Map 4" captionStartId="118.[116,166,1065,1084]" captionTargetBox="[96,1189,210,1034]" captionTargetId="figure-301@118.[96,1190,209,1034]" captionTargetPageId="118" captionText="Map 4. Localities for Slaterocoris atratus, S. fuscomarginalis, S. pilosus, S. rubrofemoratus, and S. tibialis." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5407388" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5407388/files/figure.png" pageId="115" pageNumber="115">map 4</figureCitation>
