DISCUSSION: 
<bibRefCitation author="Kelton, L. A." box="[324,495,834,856]" pageId="115" pageNumber="115" pagination="1121 - 1137" refId="ref235857" refString="Kelton, L. A. 1968. Revision of the North American species of Slaterocoris (Heteroptera: Miridae). Canadian Entomologist 100: 1121 - 1137." type="journal article" year="1968">Kelton (1968)</bibRefCitation>
